{"tid":1024054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[飛田支那雞全面上場]中國商會擬建設「大阪中華街」　盼成觀光熱點","createTime":"2019-02-16T09:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T17:42:17.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"480b0c17f21e8976d9d81fb27208b01fe2c93eb9","tid":1024054,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T09:06:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD-%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97-%E7%9B%BC%E6%88%90%E8%A7%80%E5%85%89%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7LyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=e2ab445c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&h=9ca62e2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%93%AC%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD-%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E8%A1%97-%E7%9B%BC%E6%88%90%E8%A7%80%E5%85%89%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本大阪一個由中國商人組成的「大阪華商會」，昨日提倡在大阪市西成區設立「大阪中華街」，爭取開設約100間中式餐館及商店，將西成區發展成觀光據點。不過有附近商戶就擔心會帶來垃圾及噪音問題。<br />\n<br />\n大阪華商會昨日在大阪市內一間中餐館召開會議，並宣布了「大阪中華街」的具體方面。他們希望爭取到2025年大阪關西世博會前，在西成的商店街開設共約100家中餐館、雜貨店、文化設施等，還計劃建設一個中式大門。<br />\n<br />\n包括中國駐大阪總領事李天然在內約200人參加了會議，李天然致辭說，大阪受到全球矚目，只有獲得居民的理解，才能走上繁榮與發展之路，西成能夠成為新景點。商會負責人則認為，如今的西成沒有活力，希望將把它建成眾多人來訪的觀光據點，注入活力。<br />\n<br />\n不過日本共同社引述飛田本通商店街振興協會理事長村井康夫表示，有關計劃是完全出乎意料，擔心會出現垃圾和噪音問題。毗鄰商店街的二手店經營者森雅一則表示，區內很多店舖關閉了，相信新構想會帶來活力。"},{"pid":"e0068084c5cbdb52a2433fe625600a6214b2e20e","tid":1024054,"uid":82394,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T13:11:44.000Z","msg":"西成區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2337469ab14a8fe3e523da4c404c5beabba14947","tid":1024054,"uid":35430,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"亞細亞街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ffa2f282bbfbf27bb05c852f0db974d7f7348c","tid":1024054,"uid":164387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f61bf560a1ec4d30756194c00bca39dce2c796d","tid":1024054,"uid":226524,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"去得外國就融入外國生活啦 整個中式門牌做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b0d6ce49bccd5507916185de6c0b459cc0c337","tid":1024054,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2337469ab14a8fe3e523da4c404c5beabba14947","tid":1024054,"uid":35430,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"亞細亞街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4033871aa9fb01b9c2a36171a5d4c7bffb74aa","tid":1024054,"uid":60307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"個到而家好有特色，夠哂頹"},{"pid":"9601eff03da8f80d9e47852174ec3d0e15bd8792","tid":1024054,"uid":220701,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1f61bf560a1ec4d30756194c00bca39dce2c796d","tid":1024054,"uid":226524,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"